Seattle has the same solar
footprint as Germany.

00:42:00.514 --> 00:42:02.680
And they're producing energy
so cheaply that they're

00:42:02.680 --> 00:42:04.010
exporting it to Poland.

00:42:04.010 --> 00:42:07.340
They're giving it away
at $0.01 a kilowatt.

