00:42:37.190 --> 00:42:38.062
So it's happening.

00:42:38.062 --> 00:42:39.020
We're bonding together.

00:42:39.020 --> 00:42:39.930
But you need both.

00:42:39.930 --> 00:42:40.805
You need legislation.

