He said, because he
never asked explained

00:44:28.728 --> 00:44:31.330
anybody what the problem is,
because you go to a dolphin

00:44:31.330 --> 00:44:31.830
show.

00:44:31.830 --> 00:44:33.600
And you see the dolphins
are smiling and laughing.

00:44:33.600 --> 00:44:34.930
And the kids are having fun.

00:44:34.930 --> 00:44:36.640
What's the problem?

